' comfort.</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li>He abases himself <strong>a lot</strong> to gain approval.</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li>She abases herself <strong>barely</strong> in challenging situations.</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li>We abase ourselves <strong>as</strong> little <strong>as</strong> possible.</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li>They abase themselves <strong>significantly</strong> to win trust.</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item --></ul>\n<!-- /wp:list -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Usage with Adverbs of Affirmation:</h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:list -->\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\"><!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li>I <strong>certainly</strong> refuse to abase myself for anyone.</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li>You <strong>truly</strong> abase yourself too often.</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li>He <strong>definitely</strong> abases himself in stressful situations.</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li>She <strong>undoubtedly</strong> abases herself to avoid conflict.</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li>We <strong>surely</strong> abase ourselves when it seems necessary.</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li>They <strong>certainly</strong> abase themselves for acceptance.</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item --></ul>\n<!-- /wp:list -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Usage with Adverbs of Negation:</h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:list -->\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\"><!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li>I <strong>never</strong> abase myself without a reason.</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li>You <strong>hardly</strong> ever abase yourself in front of others.</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li>He <strong>doesn\'t</strong> usually abase himself unless pressured.</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li>She <strong>won\'t</strong> abase herself just to fit in.</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li>We <strong>cannot</strong> abase ourselves without losing respect.</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li>They <strong>rarely</strong> abase themselves in their community.</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item --></ul>\n<!-- /wp:list -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Usage with Adverbs of Doubt:</h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:list -->\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\"><!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li>I <strong>might</strong> abase myself if there\'s no other option.</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li>You <strong>could</strong> abase yourself under pressure.</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li>He <strong>may</strong> abase himself if things get tough.</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li>She <strong>might</strong> abase herself to please others.</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li>We <strong>possibly</strong> abase ourselves if we see no alternatives.</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li>They <strong>might</strong> abase themselves in challenging circumstances.</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item --></ul>\n<!-- /wp:list -->','Abase (Verb) - A','','publish','open','open','','abase-verb-a','','','2024-07-26 22:59:52','2024-07-26 22:59:52','',0,'http://granjacob.com/blog/?p=25',0,'post','',0),(26,1,'2024-07-26 21:57:57','2024-07-26 21:57:57','<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>Verb: Abase</strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>Meaning:</strong> To lower in rank, office, or dignity; to humble or degrade oneself or someone else. It involves reducing someone\'s self-esteem or status, often through humiliation or belittlement.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>List 