n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Usage with Adverbs of Affirmation:</h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:list -->\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\"><!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li>I <strong>definitely begin</strong> each day with a plan.</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li>You <strong>certainly begin</strong> the project as scheduled.</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li>He <strong>undoubtedly begins</strong> his work with enthusiasm.</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li>She <strong>surely begins</strong> her tasks with determination.</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li>We <strong>absolutely begin</strong> our meetings on time.</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li>They <strong>positively begin</strong> their day with a morning routine.</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item --></ul>\n<!-- /wp:list -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Usage with Adverbs of Negation:</h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:list -->\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\"><!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li>I <strong>do not begin</strong> tasks without a strategy.</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li>You <strong>never begin</strong> your work late.</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li>He <strong>does not begin</strong> projects without preparation.</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li>She <strong>is not beginning</strong> her training until next month.</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li>We <strong>are not beginning</strong> the new initiative yet.</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li>They <strong>do not begin</strong> their work until they have all the information.</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item --></ul>\n<!-- /wp:list -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Usage with Adverbs of Doubt:</h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:list -->\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\"><!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li>I <strong>might begin</strong> the project sooner if I have time.</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li>You <strong>could begin</strong> the task earlier if necessary.</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li>He <strong>may begin</strong> the process later than planned.</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li>She <strong>might begin</strong> her new role next week.</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li>We <strong>could begin</strong> the review process at any time.</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li>They <strong>may begin</strong> their journey depending on the weather.</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item --></ul>\n<!-- /wp:list -->','Begin (Common usage Verb) - B','','publish','open','open','','begin-common-usage-verb-b','','','2024-07-26 19:53:03','2024-07-26 19:53:03','',0,'http://granjacob.com/blog/?p=45',0,'post','',0),(46,1,'2024-07-26 19:53:03','2024-07-26 19:53:03','<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>Verb: Begin</strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>Meaning:</strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:list {\"ordered\":true} -->\n<ol class=\"wp-block-list\"><!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li>To start or initiate something.</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li>To take the first step in a process or activity.</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li>To come into existence or start occurring.</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item --></ol>\n<!-- /wp:list -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>Synonyms:</strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:list -->\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\"><!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li>Start</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li>Commence</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li>Initiate</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li>Launch</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li>Embark</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item --></ul>\n<!-- /wp:list -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>Antonyms:</strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:list -->\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\"><!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li>End</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li>Finish</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li>Conclude</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li>Cease</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item --></ul>\n<!-- /wp:list -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>Usage in Different Contexts:</strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:list {\"ordered\":true} -->\n<ol class=\"wp-block-list\"><!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li><strong>Initiation Context:</strong><!-- wp:list -->\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\"><!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li><strong>Begin</strong> refers to the start of an action or event. For example: \"They began the meeting promptly.\"</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item --></ul>\n<!-- /wp:list --></li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li><strong>Process Context:</strong><!-- wp:list -->\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\"><!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li>Used to describe the start of a process or sequence. For example: \"The project began last month.\"</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item --></ul>\n<!-- /wp:list --></li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li><strong>Occurrence Context:</strong><!-- wp:list -->\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\"><!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li>Indicates the commencement of an occurrence or condition. For example: \"The symptoms began to appear suddenly.\"</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item --></ul>\n<!-- /wp:list --></li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item --></ol>\n<!-- /wp:list -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>Examples of Common Mistakes:</strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:list -->\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\"><!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li><strong>Incorrect Usage:</strong> \"She begin her new job yesterday.\"<!-- wp:list -->\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\"><!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li><strong>Correction:</strong> \"She began her new job yesterday.\"</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item --></ul>\n<!-- /wp:list --></li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li><strong>Incorrect Usage:</strong> \"The movie begin at 8 PM.\"<!-- wp:list -->\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\"><!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li><strong>Correction:</strong> \"The movie begins at 8 PM.\"</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item --></ul>\n<!-- /wp:list --></li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item --></ul>\n<!-- /wp:list -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>Collocations:</strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:list -->\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\"><!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li>Begin a project</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li>Begin a journey</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li>Begin the process</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li>Begin a new chapter</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li>Begin the meeting</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li>Begin training</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item --></ul>\n<!-- /wp:list -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Present Tense Phrases:</h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:list -->\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\"><!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li>I <strong>begin</strong> my day with a cup of coffee.</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li>You <strong>begin</strong> the course next week.</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li>He <strong>begins</strong> his work at 9 AM.</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li>She <strong>begins</strong> her new role today.</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li>We <strong>begin</strong> the project next month.</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li>They <strong>begin</strong> their vacation tomorrow.</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item --></ul>\n<!-- /wp:list -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Past Tense Phrases:</h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:list -->\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\"><!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li>I <strong>began</strong> the book last night.</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li>You <strong>began</strong> your new job last week.</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li>He <strong>began</strong> studying French in 2020.</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li>She <strong>began</strong> her journey to success years ago.</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li>We <strong>began</strong> the meeting on time yesterday.</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li>They <strong>began</strong> their vacation last summer.</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item --></ul>\n<!-- /wp:list -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Future Tense Phrases:</h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:list -->\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\"><!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li>I <strong>will begin</strong> my new job next Monday.</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li>You <strong>will begin</strong> the course in the fall.</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li>He <strong>will begin</strong> his training next month.</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li>She <strong>will begin</strong> her studies abroad next year.</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li>We <strong>will begin</strong> the project as soon as possible.</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li>They <strong>will begin</strong> their holiday in December.</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item --></ul>\n<!-- /wp:list -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Usage with Adverbs of Frequency:</h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:list -->\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\"><!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li>I <strong>always begin</strong> my day with exercise.</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li>You <stro