ur offerings:</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:list -->\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\"><!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li><strong>Hotel Management:</strong><br>Our all-in-one hotel management solution streamlines operations, enhances guest experiences, and optimizes resource management. From booking and reservations to housekeeping and analytics, we provide the tools you need to deliver exceptional hospitality services.</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li><strong>Neptuneql:</strong><br>Unlock the full potential of your data with Neptuneql, our advanced data management and analysis solution. With intuitive interfaces and powerful capabilities, Neptuneql enables you to harness structured information, driving informed decision-making and gaining a competitive edge.</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li><strong>Financial Services:</strong><br>Simplify complex financial processes with our specialized services for managing compound interest investments. We provide clarity and control over your financial strategies, allowing you to make the most of your investment opportunities without the complexity of traditional platforms.</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li><strong>Learn English:</strong><br>Empower individuals and organizations with our comprehensive English learning solutions. Tailored to meet the needs of learners at all levels, our programs help improve language skills, enhance communication, and open doors to new opportunities.</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li><strong>Employment and Recruitment Solutions:</strong><br>Connect talent with opportunity through our efficient employment and recruitment services. We facilitate seamless interactions between job seekers and employers, ensuring the right fit for both parties across a variety of industries and roles.</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li><strong>Software Development:</strong><br>Bring your ideas to life with our custom software development services. From initial concept to final deployment, our team of experienced developers works closely with you to create innovative, scalable solutions that meet your unique business requirements.</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li><strong>Schedule System Service:</strong><br>Simplify appointment scheduling and service delivery with our advanced schedule system. Designed to facilitate seamless meeting arrangements and service coordination, our solution enhances efficiency and ensures a smooth experience for both providers and clients.</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item --></ul>\n<!-- /wp:list -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>At GRAN JACOB, we believe in the power of technology to drive success. Our solutions are designed to help you navigate the challenges of today and seize the opportunities of tomorrow. Partner with us and experience the difference of working with a company dedicated to your success.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->','Services','','publish','closed','closed','','services','','','2024-08-02 01:19:38','2024-08-02 01:19:38','',127,'http://granjacob.com/blog/?page_id=86',2,'page','',0),(87,1,'2024-07-30 02:59:38','2024-07-30 02:59:38','<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Servicios</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->','Services','','inherit','closed','closed','','86-revision-v1','','','2024-07-30 02:59:38','2024-07-30 02:59:38','',86,'http://granjacob.com/blog/?p=87',0,'revision','',0),(88,1,'2024-07-30 03:10:19','0000-00-00 00:00:00','','Auto Draft','','auto-draft','closed','closed','','','','','2024-07-30 03:10:19','0000-00-00 00:00:00','',0,'http://granjacob.com/blog/?page_id=88',0,'page','',0),(89,1,'2024-07-30 03:18:58','2024-07-30 03:18:58','<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Welcome to GRAN JACOB S.A.S, a company born from passion, innovation, and a commitment to excellence. Our story is one of transformation and resilience, driven by the belief that technology can create meaningful change for businesses and communities alike.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Our Foundation</h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>GRAN JACOB was originally founded in 2009 by Cristian Jimenez under the name CRISHK. With a focus on website development, domain sales, hosting, and software development, CRISHK aimed to make a mark in the competitive digital landscape. Despite initial challenges and an eventual closure in 2017, Cristian’s journey was far from over.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Following the closure of CRISHK, Cristian spent several years honing his skills and gaining valuable experience as an employee at three different companies in Colombia, including a significant tenure at TATA Consultancy Services, where he contributed to major projects with Bancolombia and Avianca.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>In July 2024, inspired by his son Jacob, Cristian decided to refound his company with renewed purpose and vision. The name GRAN JACOB symbolizes greatness and inspiration, with “GRAN” reflecting our ambition to achieve greatness and “JACOB” honoring the profound impact of Cristian\'s son on his life and work.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Our Mission</h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>At GRAN JACOB, our mission is to be the best in everything we do. We strive to deliver exceptional SaaS solutions that meet the evolving needs of our clients, empowering businesses to achieve their goals with confidence and efficiency. Our commitment extends beyond business success to include philanthropic efforts that contribute to the well-being of our community and society at large.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Our Vision</h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Our vision is to become a leading force in the global market, recognized for our innovative solutions and unwavering dedication to excellence. We aim to be a trusted partner for businesses and individuals, providing the tools and support needed to navigate the challenges of today and seize the opportunities of tomorrow.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Our Values</h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>At GRAN JACOB, we hold ourselves to the highest standards of integrity and professionalism. Our core values include:</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:list -->\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\"><!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li><strong>Honesty:</strong> We believe in transparent and honest communication with our clients, partners, and employees. Trust is the foundation of our relationships, and we are committed to maintaining it.</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li><strong>Integrity:</strong> We uphold the highest ethical standards, ensuring that our actions align with our principles. We are dedicated to doing what is right, even when faced with challenges.</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li><strong>Innovation:</strong> We are passionate about exploring new ideas and embracing change. Our commitment to innovation drives us to deliver cutting-edge solutions that meet the needs of our clients.</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li><strong>Excellence:</strong> We strive for excellence in every aspect of our business, from the quality of our services to the satisfaction of our clients. Our goal is to exceed expectations and set new benchmarks for success.</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li><strong>Collaboration:</strong> We believe in the power of teamwork and collaboration. By working together, we can achieve more and create solutions that are greater than the sum of their parts.</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li><strong>Commitment:</strong> We are committed to our clients, our community, and our vision for the future. Our dedication to continuous improvement ensures that we remain at the forefront of our industry.</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item --></ul>\n<!-- /wp:list -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Join us on our journey to greatness. At GRAN JACOB, we are inspired by the past, driven by the present, and excited for the future. Together, let\'s create a world where technology empowers and uplifts everyone.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->','About Us','','publish','closed','closed','','about-us-2','','','2024-08-02 01:19:34','2024-08-02 01:19:34','',127,'http://granjacob.com/blog/?page_id=89',1,'page','',0),(90,1,'2024-07-30 03:17:19','2024-07-30 03:17:19','<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Welcome to GRAN JACOB S.A.S</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>GRAN JACOB S.A.S specializes in SaaS (Software as a Servicce), our business core is focused in software development and create tools and projects for the people and companies.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->','About Us','','inherit','closed','closed','','89-revision-v1','','','2024-07-30 03:17:19','2024-07-30 03:17:19','',89,'http://granjacob.com/blog/?p=90',0,'revision','',0),(91,1,'2024-07-30 03:18:58','2024-07-30 03:18:58','<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Welcome to GRAN JACOB S.A.S</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>GRAN JACOB S.A.S specializes in SaaS (Software as a Servicce), our business core is focused in software development and create tools and projects for the people and companies.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Actually we are working in a database language and application generation system. This projects involves task of investigation and development of algorithm with Open AI to achieve our goals. </p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->','About Us','','inherit','closed','closed','','89-revision-v1','','','2024-07-30 03:18:58','2024-07-30 03:18:58','',89,'http://granjacob.com/blog/?p=91',0,'revision','',0),(92,1,'2024-07-30 03:20:29','2024-07-30 03:20:29','<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>At GRAN JACOB, we are dedicated to transforming industries with our innovative Software as a Service (SaaS) solutions. As a dynamic and forward-thinking company, we are committed to helping businesses thrive in an ever-changing digital landscape. Our diverse range of services is designed to meet the unique needs of various sectors, ensuring that your business stays ahead of the curve.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>We believe in the power of technology to drive success. Our team of experts is dedicated to delivering exceptional service and innovative solutions that cater to the evolving needs of businesses and individuals alike. Join us on our journey to redefine what\'s possible in the world of SaaS.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>Why Choose GRAN JACOB?</strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:list -->\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\"><!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li><strong>Customer-Centric Approach:</strong> We prioritize our clients, ensuring that our solutions are tailored to meet their specific requirements and exceed their expectations.</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li><strong>Innovation:</strong> We embrace innovation and continuously seek new ways to enhance our services and deliver value to our clients.</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li><strong>Expertise:</strong> Our team is composed of industry experts who are passionate about their work and committed to providing top-tier solutions.</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li><strong>Versatility:</strong> With a wide array of services, we cater to multiple business areas, offering versatile solutions that adapt to the ever-changing market landscape.</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item --></ul>\n<!-- /wp:list -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Partner with GRAN JACOB and experience the difference of working with a company that is as invested in your success as you are. Let us help you navigate the challenges of today and seize the opportunities of tomorrow.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->','Welcome','','publish','closed','closed','','home','','','2024-08-02 01:22:44','2024-08-02 01:22:44','',127,'http://granjacob.com/blog/?page_id=92',0,'page','',0),(93,1,'2024-07-30 03:20:29','2024-07-30 03:20:29','<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Home information</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->','Home','','inherit','closed','closed','','92-revision-v1','','','2024-07-30 03:20:29','2024-07-30 03:20:29','',92,'http://granjacob.com/blog/?p=93',0,'revision','',0),(94,1,'2024-07-30 05:05:27','2024-07-30 05:05:27','<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Contact us with the following information:</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Phone: +57 3206767632 </p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Email: </p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:list -->\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\"><!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li>granjacob8317@gmail.com</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li>support@granjacob.com</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item --></ul>\n<!-- /wp:list -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Location: Medellin, Colombia.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->','Contact','','inherit','closed','closed','','84-revision-v1','','','2024-07-30 05:05:27','2024-07-30 05:05:27','',84,'http://granjacob.com/blog/?p=94',0,'revision','',0),(95,1,'2024-07-30 17:46:01','2024-07-30 17:46:01','<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><span style=\"background-color: var(--wp--preset--color--background); color: var(--wp--preset--color--foreground); font-family: var(--wp--preset--font-family--jost); font-size: var(--wp-preset--font-size--small);\">At GRAN JACOB, we are committed to transforming innovative ideas into powerful solutions that drive success for our clients. Our projects are designed with the future in mind, leveraging cutting-edge technology and cloud services to deliver high-quality applications that meet the diverse needs of businesses worldwide.</span><p>Our projects are built on Amazon Web Services (AWS) infrastructure, ensuring scalability, security, and reliability. To showcase our work and share our progress with the world, we use micro-websites and full-scale websites to promote and demo our projects online.</p><h3>Current Projects</h3><h4>Neptuneql</h4><p><strong>Status:</strong> 30% Complete</p><p>Neptuneql is our flagship project and represents a significant milestone in our mission to revolutionize data management and application development. This groundbreaking platform is designed to simplify the creation and management of entities and their relationships, providing a robust framework for developing applications across various programming languages.</p><p><strong>Key Features:</strong></p><ul><li><p><strong>Entity and Relationship Management:</strong> Easily create and manage complex data models with intuitive interfaces and powerful tools.</p></li><li><p><strong>Attribute Properties Mapping:</strong> Define and customize attribute properties for each entity, enabling precise control over data structures and behavior.</p></li><li><p><strong>Application Generation:</strong> Automatically generate applications in multiple programming languages, streamlining development and reducing time to market.</p></li><li><p><strong>Scalability and Flexibility:</strong> Designed to grow with your business, Neptuneql provides the flexibility to adapt to changing requirements and support future expansion.</p></li></ul><p>Neptuneql is the foundation upon which we will build our next generation of projects. As we continue to enhance its capabilities, we are committed to delivering a platform that empowers businesses to harness the full potential of their data.</p><h3>Future Vision</h3><p>As our projects evolve, our goal is to transform them into fully-fledged services that deliver exceptional value to our clients. By leveraging the latest advancements in technology and cloud services, we aim to provide scalable, efficient, and user-friendly solutions that meet the unique needs of each business we serve.</p><p>At GRAN JACOB, we are passionate about pushing the boundaries of what\'s possible and redefining the future of technology. Join us on our journey as we continue to innovate and create solutions that drive success for businesses around the globe.</p></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->','Projects','','publish','closed','closed','','projects','','','2024-08-02 01:19:43','2024-08-02 01:19:43','',127,'http://granjacob.com/blog/?page_id=95',3,'page','',0),(96,1,'2024-07-30 17:46:01','2024-07-30 17:46:01','','Projects','','inherit','closed','closed','','95-revision-v1','','','2024-07-30 17:46:01','2024-07-30 17:46:01','',95,'http://granjacob.com/blog/?p=96',0,'revision','',0),(97,1,'2024-07-30 17:47:23','0000-00-00 00:00:00','','Auto Draft','','auto-draft','closed','closed','','','','','2024-07-30 17:47:23','0000-00-00 00:00:00','',0,'http://granjacob.com/blog/?page_id=97',0,'page','',0),(98,1,'2024-07-30 17:49:14','2024-07-30 17:49:14','','Home','','publish','closed','closed','','home','','','2024-07-30 17:49:14','2024-07-30 17:49:14','',0,'http://granjacob.com/blog/?page_id=98',0,'page','',0),(99,1,'2024-07-30 17:49:14','2024-07-30 17:49:14','','Home','','inherit','closed','closed','','98-revision-v1','','','2024-07-30 17:49:14','2024-07-30 17:49:14','',98,'http://granjacob.com/blog/?p=99',0,'revision','',0),(101,1,'2024-07-30 22:27:20','2024-07-30 22:27:20','<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>At GRAN JACOB, we are dedicated to transforming industries with our innovative Software as a Service (SaaS) solutions. As a dynamic and forward-thinking company, we are committed to helping businesses thrive in an ever-changing digital landscape. Our diverse range of services is designed to meet the unique nee