ons to housekeeping and analytics, we provide the tools you need to deliver exceptional hospitality services.</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li><strong>Neptuneql:</strong><br>Unlock the full potential of your data with Neptuneql, our advanced data management and analysis solution. With intuitive interfaces and powerful capabilities, Neptuneql enables you to harness structured information, driving informed decision-making and gaining a competitive edge.</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li><strong>Financial Services:</strong><br>Simplify complex financial processes with our specialized services for managing compound interest investments. We provide clarity and control over your financial strategies, allowing you to make the most of your investment opportunities without the complexity of traditional platforms.</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li><strong>Learn English:</strong><br>Empower individuals and organizations with our comprehensive English learning solutions. Tailored to meet the needs of learners at all levels, our programs help improve language skills, enhance communication, and open doors to new opportunities.</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li><strong>Employment and Recruitment Solutions:</strong><br>Connect talent with opportunity through our efficient employment and recruitment services. We facilitate seamless interactions between job seekers and employers, ensuring the right fit for both parties across a variety of industries and roles.</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li><strong>Software Development:</strong><br>Bring your ideas to life with our custom software development services. From initial concept to final deployment, our team of experienced developers works closely with you to create innovative, scalable solutions that meet your unique business requirements.</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li><strong>Schedule System Service:</strong><br>Simplify appointment scheduling and service delivery with our advanced schedule system. Designed to facilitate seamless meeting arrangements and service coordination, our solution enhances efficiency and ensures a smooth experience for both providers and clients.</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item --></ul>\n<!-- /wp:list -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>At GRAN JACOB, we believe in the power of technology to drive success. Our solutions are designed to help you navigate the challenges of today and seize the opportunities of tomorrow. Partner with us and experience the difference of working with a company dedicated to your success.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->','Services','','inherit','closed','closed','','86-revision-v1','','','2024-07-30 23:37:37','2024-07-30 23:37:37','',86,'http://granjacob.com/blog/?p=115',0,'revision','',0),(116,1,'2024-07-31 01:24:12','2024-07-31 01:24:12','<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>At GRAN JACOB, we are dedicated to transforming industries with our innovative Software as a Service (SaaS) solutions. As a dynamic and forward-thinking company, we are committed to helping businesses thrive in an ever-changing digital landscape. Our diverse range of services is designed to meet the unique needs of various sectors, ensuring that your business stays ahead of the curve.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>We believe in the power of technology to drive success. Our team of experts is dedicated to delivering exceptional service and innovative solutions that cater to the evolving needs of businesses and individuals alike. Join us on our journey to redefine what\'s possible in the world of SaaS.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>Why Choose GRAN JACOB?</strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:list -->\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\"><!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li><strong>Customer-Centric Approach:</strong> We prioritize our clients, ensuring that our solutions are tailored to meet their specific requirements and exceed their expectations.</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li><strong>Innovation:</strong> We embrace innovation and continuously seek new ways to enhance our services and deliver value to our clients.</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li><strong>Expertise:</strong> Our team is composed of industry experts who are passionate about their work and committed to providing top-tier solutions.</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li><strong>Versatility:</strong> With a wide array of services, we cater to multiple business areas, offering versatile solutions that adapt to the ever-changing market landscape.</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item --></ul>\n<!-- /wp:list -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Partner with GRAN JACOB and experience the difference of working with a company that is as invested in your success as you are. Let us help you navigate the challenges of today and seize the opportunities of tomorrow.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->','Welcome','','inherit','closed','closed','','92-revision-v1','','','2024-07-31 01:24:12','2024-07-31 01:24:12','',92,'http://granjacob.com/blog/?p=116',0,'revision','',0),(117,1,'2024-07-31 11:56:08','2024-07-31 11:56:08','<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><span style=\"background-color: var(--wp--preset--color--background); color: var(--wp--preset--color--foreground); font-family: var(--wp--preset--font-family--jost); font-size: var(--wp-preset--font-size--small);\">At GRAN JACOB, we are committed to transforming innovative ideas into powerful solutions that drive success for our clients. Our projects are designed with the future in mind, leveraging cutting-edge technology and cloud services to deliver high-quality applications that meet the diverse needs of businesses worldwide.</span><p>Our projects are built on Amazon Web Services (AWS) infrastructure, ensuring scalability, security, and reliability. To showcase our work and share our progress with the world, we use micro-websites and full-scale websites to promote and demo our projects online.</p><h3>Current Projects</h3><h4>Neptuneql</h4><p><strong>Status:</strong> 30% Complete</p><p>Neptuneql is our flagship project and represents a significant milestone in our mission to revolutionize data management and application development. This groundbreaking platform is designed to simplify the creation and management of entities and their relationships, providing a robust framework for developing applications across various programming languages.</p><p><strong>Key Features:</strong></p><ul><li><p><strong>Entity and Relationship Management:</strong> Easily create and manage complex data models with intuitive interfaces and powerful tools.</p></li><li><p><strong>Attribute Properties Mapping:</strong> Define and customize attribute properties for each entity, enabling precise control over data structures and behavior.</p></li><li><p><strong>Application Generation:</strong> Automatically generate applications in multiple programming languages, streamlining development and reducing time to market.</p></li><li><p><strong>Scalability and Flexibility:</strong> Designed to grow with your business, Neptuneql provides the flexibility to adapt to changing requirements and support future expansion.</p></li></ul><p>Neptuneql is the foundation upon which we will build our next generation of projects. As we continue to enhance its capabilities, we are committed to delivering a platform that empowers businesses to harness the full potential of their data.</p><h3>Future Vision</h3><p>As our projects evolve, our goal is to transform them into fully-fledged services that deliver exceptional value to our clients. By leveraging the latest advancements in technology and cloud services, we aim to provide scalable, efficient, and user-friendly solutions that meet the unique needs of each business we serve.</p><p>At GRAN JACOB, we are passionate about pushing the boundaries of what\'s possible and redefining the future of technology. Join us on our journey as we continue to innovate and create solutions that drive success for businesses around the globe.</p></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->','Projects','','inherit','closed','closed','','95-revision-v1','','','2024-07-31 11:56:08','2024-07-31 11:56:08','',95,'http://granjacob.com/blog/?p=117',0,'revision','',0),(118,1,'2024-07-31 12:00:49','2024-07-31 12:00:49','<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>Last updated:</strong> 29/JUL/2024</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Welcome to GRAN JACOB. We are committed to protecting your privacy and ensuring that your personal information is handled in a safe and responsible manner. This privacy policy outlines how we collect, use, disclose, and protect your information when you visit our website or use our services. By using our website, you agree to the terms outlined in this policy.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\">1. <strong>Information We Collect</strong></h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>We may collect the following types of information:</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":4} -->\n<h4 class=\"wp-block-heading\">1.1 <strong>Personal Information</strong></h4>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:list -->\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\"><!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li><strong>Contact Details:</strong> Name, email address, phone number, and address.</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li><strong>Account Information:</strong> Username, password, and other credentials.</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li><strong>Communication Preferences:</strong> Details about your preferences for receiving communications from us.</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item --></ul>\n<!-- /wp:list -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":4} -->\n<h4 class=\"wp-block-heading\">1.2 <strong>Non-Personal Information</strong></h4>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:list -->\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\"><!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li><strong>Device Information:</strong> IP address, browser type, operating system, and device identifiers.</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li><strong>Usage Data:</strong> Information about how you use our website, such as pages visited, time spent, and interaction data.</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item --></ul>\n<!-- /wp:list -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\">2. <strong>How We Use Your Information</strong></h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>We use your information for the following purposes:</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:list -->\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\"><!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li><strong>To Provide Services:</strong> To process transactions, manage accounts, and provide customer support.</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li><strong>To Improve Our Website:</strong> To analyze usage patterns and improve our website’s functionality and user experience.</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li><strong>To Communicate:</strong> To send newsletters, updates, and promotional materials, and to respond to inquiries.</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li><strong>To Comply with Legal Obligations:</strong> To meet regulatory requirements and enforce our legal rights.</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item --></ul>\n<!-- /wp:list -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\">3. <strong>Sharing Your Information</strong></h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>We may share your information with third parties in the following circumstances:</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:list -->\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\"><!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li><strong>Service Providers:</strong> We may share your information with trusted service providers who assist us in operating our website and providing our services.</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li><strong>Legal Compliance:</strong> We may disclose your information to comply with legal obligations or respond to lawful requests from public authorities.</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li><strong>Business Transfers:</strong> In the event of a merger, acquisition, or sale of assets, your information may be transferred to the new owners.</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item --></ul>\n<!-- /wp:list -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\">4. <strong>International Data Transfers</strong></h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>We comply with applicable legal requirements for transferring personal information to countries outside of Colombia and the European Economic Area (EEA). When we transfer information internationally, we ensure appropriate safeguards are in place to protect your data.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\">5. <strong>Data Security</strong></h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>We implement appropriate technical and organizational measures to protect your information from unauthorized access, alteration, disclosure, or destruction. While we strive to protect your data, no transmission over the internet is completely secure, and we cannot guarantee absolute security.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\">6. <strong>Your Rights</strong></h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>You have the following rights concerning your personal data:</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:list -->\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\"><!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li><strong>Access:</strong> You have the right to request access to the personal information we hold about you.</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li><strong>Rectification:</strong> You have the right to request correction of inaccurate or incomplete information.</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li><strong>Deletion:</strong> You have the right to request deletion of your personal information under certain conditions.</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li><strong>Objection:</strong> You have the right to object to the processing of your data for specific purposes.</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li><strong>Data Portability:</strong> You have the right to request the transfer of your data to another organization or directly to you.</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item --></ul>\n<!-- /wp:list -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>To exercise your rights, please contact us using the contact information provided below.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\">7. <strong>Cookies and Tracking Technologies</strong></h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Our website uses cookies and similar technologies to enhance your browsing experience. You can choose to accept or decline cookies through your browser settings. However, declining cookies may limit your ability to use certain features of our website.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\">8. <strong>Third-Party Links</strong></h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Our website may contain links to third-party websites. We are not responsible for the privacy practices or content of these sites. We encourage you to review the privacy policies of any third-party sites you visit.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\">9. <strong>Children\'s Privacy</strong></h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Our services are not intended for individuals under the age of 18. We do not knowingly collect personal information from children without parental consent. If we become aware that we have collected personal information from a child, we will take steps to delete such information promptly.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\">10. <strong>Changes to This Privacy Policy</strong></h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>We may update this privacy policy from time to time to reflect changes in our practices or legal obligations. We will notify you of any material changes by posting the updated policy on our website. We encourage you to review this policy periodically.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\">11. <strong>Contact Us</strong></h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>If you have any questions or concerns about this privacy policy or our data practices, please contact us at:</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:list -->\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\"><!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li><strong>Email:</strong> <a>granjacob8317@gmail.com</a> / <a>support@granjacob.com</a></li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li><strong>Phone:</strong> +57 3206767632</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li><strong>Address:</strong> Medellín, Colombia</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item --></ul>\n<!-- /wp:list -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Legal Compliance</h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>This privacy policy is designed to comply with the following regulations:</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:list -->\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\"><!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li><strong>Colombian Law 1581 of 2012:</strong> Protects personal data in Colombia and outlines principles for handling personal information.</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li><strong>GDPR (General Data Protection Regulation):</strong> A European Union regulation that provides guidelines for the collection and processing of personal information.</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item --></ul>\n<!-- /wp:list -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>By using our services, you consent to the collection and use of your information as outlined in this policy. We are committed to ensuring your privacy and protecting your personal data with the highest level of care.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->','Privacy Policy','','publish','closed','closed','','privacy-policy','','','2024-08-02 01:21:15','2024-08-02 01:21:15','',121,'http://granjacob.com/blog/?page_id=118',0,'page','',0),(119,1,'2024-07-31 12:00:49','2024-07-31 12:00:49','<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>Last updated:</strong> 29/JUL/2024</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Welcome to GRAN JACOB. We are committed to protecting your privacy and ensuring that your personal information is handled in a safe and responsible manner. This privacy policy outlines how we collect, use, disclose, and protect your information when you visit our website or use our services. By using our website, you agree to the terms outlined in this policy.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\">1. <strong>Information We Collect</strong></h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>We may collect the following types of information:</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":4} -->\n<h4 class=\"wp-block-heading\">1.1 <strong>Personal Information</strong></h4>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:list -->\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\"><!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li><strong>Contact Details:</strong> Name, email address, phone number, and address.</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li><strong>Account Information:</strong> Username, password, and other credentials.</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li><strong>Communication Preferences:</strong> Details about your preferences for receiving communications from us.</li>\n<!-- /wp:list