ong> Aligns with Law 1581 of 2012, addressing personal data protection and user rights in Colombia.</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li><strong>GDPR (General Data Protection Regulation):</strong> Complies with EU regulations to protect personal data and privacy.</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item --></ul>\n<!-- /wp:list -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>Note:</strong> This document is a general guideline. It is recommended to consult with legal counsel to ensure that your Terms of Use are fully compliant with local and international laws applicable to your business.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->','Terms of use','','publish','closed','closed','','terms-of-use','','','2024-08-02 01:21:23','2024-08-02 01:21:23','',121,'http://granjacob.com/blog/?page_id=123',0,'page','',0),(124,1,'2024-07-31 12:04:45','2024-07-31 12:04:45','<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>Last updated:</strong> [Date]</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Welcome to the GRAN JACOB website. By accessing or using our website and services, you agree to comply with and be bound by these Terms of Use. Please read them carefully before using our website. If you do not agree with these terms, you should not use our website or services.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\">1. <strong>Acceptance of Terms</strong></h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>By accessing or using our website, you acknowledge that you have read, understood, and agree to be bound by these Terms of Use, along with our <a href=\"#\">Privacy Policy</a>. If you are using our website on behalf of a company or other legal entity, you represent that you have the authority to bind that entity to these terms.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\">2. <strong>Eligibility</strong></h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Our services are intended for users who a